<li id="cite_note-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFJacquart">Jacquart, Danielle, "The Influence of Arabic Medicine in the Medieval West", pp.&#160;980</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=The+Influence+of+Arabic+Medicine+in+the+Medieval+West&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Jacquart&amp;rft.aufirst=Danielle&amp;rft.au=Jacquart%2C+Danielle&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B980&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Melancholia"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> in <cite class="inline">(<a href="#CITEREFMorrisonRashed1996" title="">Morrison &amp; Rashed 1996</a>, pp.&#160;963-84)</cite></li>
